divs: Sighting Details* UFO is right above the mountains. After a storm, I was out taking pix of the mountains, with the clouds rolling over them. I took lots of pix and did not go thru them until I got home and had downloaded them on to my computer. I did not notice this unidentified object until I was looking thru the photos on my laptop. It does not look like a bird and it appears to have a strong shadow underneath it. I am not claiming it's a UFO, but it doesn't look like anything I recognize. Do you know anyone that can analyze this photo and give an opinion?
